snippet.title: Ori and The Will of The Wisps – Nintendo Switch Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
iam8bit has teamed up with Moon Studios and Microsoft Game Studios to bring Ori and the Will of the Wisps to the Nintendo Switch. The critically acclaimed sequel to Ori and the Blind Forest is available today on the Nintendo eShop!

And to celebrate Ori's 5th anniversary, iam8bit and Moon Studios have crafted a gorgeous Physical Collector's Edition, which includes Ori and the Will of the Wisps + Ori and the Blind Forest. Pre-order now at https://ori.iam8bit.com/
